### 4. **Mock Handle Files:**

#### `src/test/mock-handle.ts` (Lines 1-123)
```typescript
export function createMockHandle(): WorldHandle & {
  triggerGuildEvent(event: GuildEvent): void;
  // ... other trigger methods
} {
